Date:- 12.03.2025

Practical No:- 06

Problem Specification:- How to Print the student's details using \n newline character in java.

Implementation:-
class Exercise6{
	public static void main(String args[]){
	System.out.println("First Name:Theebiga \nLast Name:Pushpakaran \nAddress:Columbuhurai,Jaffna");
	}
}
Output:-
First Name: Theebiga
Last Name: Pushpakaran
Address: Columbuthurai,Jaffna

Conclusion:-I learnt to use \n new line character which allow us to format the output by printing on a separate line.
 

 
